data.description: REDUCED ELECTRIC BILLS WITH NEW SOLAR PANELS!!! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Port Charlotte. With a BRAND-NEW ROOF, updated IMPACT WINDOWS, and the 50 AMP GENERATOR hook-up, this property offers peace of mind and energy efficiency for years to come. Embrace eco-friendly living with solar panels adorning the roof, providing sustainable energy and reducing your carbon footprint. Step into the spacious backyard and you'll find an inviting above-ground pool, ideal for relaxation and entertaining, all within the privacy of a fenced-in yard and oversized screened in lanai. Inside, the kitchen features wood cabinets, Quartz counters, and an inviting eat-in area. The impact windows installed in 2023 offer natural light and views of the beautiful backyard. The guest bedrooms can also be used as an office or craft room, or perfect for out of town guests. With the HVAC system updated in 2020 and the roof installed in 2023, you'll stay comfortable in every season. Enjoy the beauty of Florida's outdoor living year-round in the screened-in lanai, an excellent spot for sipping morning coffee or hosting evening gatherings . Extra storage space with 2 sheds and a convenient carport ensure that your belongings and vehicles are well-protected. Don't miss the chance to call this Port Charlotte gem your home, where modern amenities and timeless charm blend seamlessly. Close to shopping, restaurants, beaches, and the Harborwalk, explore this property today, and make it your Florida dream home.
